      <td>Story points — a <strong>fully separate</strong> estimation field</td>
      <td>Bug is a <em>value</em> of the single type axis, not a parallel field</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Linear</td>
      <td>One structural item (Issue) + parent/sub-issue for hierarchy</td>
