    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>GitLab</td>
      <td>One <em>issue type</em> (issue / incident / task / epic)</td>
      <td>Separate <em>weight</em></td>
      <td>Free-form <em>labels</em></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td><strong>WE today</strong></td>
      <td><strong>Two</strong> — <code>type</code> (nature) <em>and</em> <code>workItem</code> (role), 1:1 correlated</td>
